headline: Is There Still Upside in Jabil After Major Business Divestiture and a 41% Surge in 2025?
summary: Thinking about whether Jabil is a good value right now? You are not alone. Investors are eager to know if there is still upside after such a strong run. Jabil’s shares have surged an impressive 449.4% over the last five years, and even after a 5.5% slip this past week, the stock is still up 41.3% year-to-date. Recently, Jabil announced the successful completion of a major business divestiture. This has sparked fresh investor interest and speculation about how the company's streamlined...
